  "body": "### Problem\nIn Teller Network, if a user has already added another user to their contacts, and then see their offers in the list of offers, they should be able to see that user's profile picture instead of the identicon. \n\nCurrently we do not have a way to obtain that profile picture, the API does not provide such functionality, which would be useful not only for Teller Network, but for any DApp that wishes to have a greater level of integration with the Status App\n\n### Suggested Implementation\n\n\n```\nwindow.ethereum.status\n.getProfilePicture(\"0xCONTACT_PUBLIC_KEY_GOES_HERE\")\n.then(image => {\nconsole.log('Base64 Image data:', image);\n})\n```\n\n",
